A Super-Friday at Japan ends with golden brooch or silver tray.
An adorable Rushia has appeared today. :_ハート:

2:31:42 At ending the normal stream, followed the Supaachaato Orei Time, but Rushia forgot something... It was... 
The LiveChat noticed her...

2:33:40 "Enchanting Waltz" (Rushia stream's ending, premiered at 2020 May 31st, but officially released at 2020 June 5th) plays... Rushia makes comments and laughs uncontrollably. :_くさｗ:

Repeats time later, at 5:05:35 at finishing "Supaachaato Orei Time" part. 

5:06:04 Party's epilogue. (Some fellow fans, fandeads and followers calls it as "Part C")  :_るんるん:

An unforgettable and lovely night :_るんるん: :_ちょうちょ:

:_ちょうちょ: Uruha Rushia's Original Character Design by Yasuyuki-sensei 
:_ハート: Live2D modeling by Tou Ilie 
Please contact Yasuyuki-sensei and his secretary at Twitter: "yasu00kamiki" and "chiyogamimi"
